  "title": "General Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>Job Description: General Cleaner</p><p>Job Title: General Cleaner / Cleaning Attendant</p><p>Location: West / Island-wide</p><p>Working Hours: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM / Shift Work</p><p>Employment Type: Full-time / Part-time</p><p></p><p>Role Overview</p><p>We are looking for a reliable Cleaner to join our team. You will be responsible for maintaining cleanliness and hygiene at our assigned sites (Offices / Residential Blocks).</p><p>We welcome seniors and candidates with no prior experience to apply. Training will be provided.</p><p>Responsibilities</p><p>•\tGeneral Cleaning: Sweeping, mopping, and vacuuming of floors.</p><p>•\tWaste Management: Clearing trash bins and replacing bin liners.</p><p>•\tRestroom Hygiene: Washing and sanitizing toilets, refilling soap, and toilet paper.</p><p>•\tSurface Cleaning: Wiping down tables, windows, glass panels, and high-touch points (doorknobs, lift buttons).</p><p>•\tPantry Maintenance: Washing cups (if applicable) and keeping the pantry area tidy.</p><p>•\tAd-hoc Duties: Assisting with periodic deep cleaning or spot cleaning as instructed by the Supervisor.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>•\tExperience: No experience required; on-the-job training is provided.</p><p>•\tPhysical Health: Must be physically fit to stand, walk, and perform cleaning duties.</p><p>•\tAttitude: Punctual, responsible, and able to work independently.</p><p>•\tLanguage: Basic English, Mandarin, Malay, or Tamil is acceptable.</p><p>•\tCertifications: Having existing WSQ Cleaning Certificates is a bonus (but not a must; we will send you for training).</p><p>Salary & Benefits</p><p>•\tGross Salary: SGD 1,740 - SGD 2,500.</p><p>•\tLeave: Annual Leave, Medical Leave, and Hospitalization Leave.</p><p>•\tBonus: Annual Wage Supplement (AWS) / Performance Bonus.</p><p>•\tAllowances: Transport allowance.</p>",
